name: RecordLabels
desc: A resource object that represents a record label.

items.name: id
items.desc: The identifier for the record label.

items.name: type
items.desc: This value must always be record-labels.

items.name: href
items.desc: A relative location for the record label resource.

items.name: attributes
items.desc: The attributes of the record label.

items.name: views
items.desc: The relationship views for the record label.
